	<h3>Related Documents</h3>      
	<ul>
	
	<li><a href="/en/government_in_ireland/european_government/eu_institutions/european_parliament.html">European Parliament</a><br>The European Parliament represents about 502 million people in the 28 countries of the European Union.</li>
	
